OL,3,CEmergency care disruption after power
OL,4,Ccut at hospital
OL,6,FThe Great Western Hospitals NHS
OL,7,FFoundation Trust in Swindon could see
OL,8,Fdisruption on Wednesday 10 July due a
OL,9,Fpower outage which last several hours
OL,10,Fon Tuesday 9 July.
OL,12,FDozens of planned operations were
OL,13,Fpostponed.
OL,15,FIn a post on X, formerly known as
OL,16,FTwitter, the trust said at 3.17pm that
OL,17,Fits emergency department and urgent
OL,18,Ftreatment centre were also affected by
OL,19,Fthe outage.
