OL,6,FIt advised patients with a serious
OL,7,Fmedical issue to call NHS 111 or 999,
OL,8,Fdepending on the severity of their
OL,9,Fcondition.
OL,11,F"Planned appointments are currently
OL,12,Fpostponed. If you have a planned
OL,13,Fappointment at the hospital today,
OL,14,Fplease do not attend and we will
OL,15,Fcontact you at the earliest
OL,16,Fopportunity to re-arrange. Our
OL,17,Fswitchboard is currently also
OL,18,Faffected," the trust said.
