OL,3,CEmergency care disruption after power
OL,4,Ccut at hospital
OL,6,FIn at update issued at 8.30pm on
OL,7,FTuesday 9 July, the trust said:
OL,8,F"Following a power outage earlier
OL,9,Ftoday, power across the Great Western
OL,10,FHospital has been restored.
OL,12,F"We are expecting our Urgent and
OL,13,FEmergency Care Services to be very
OL,14,Fbusy in the coming days and are
OL,15,Fadvising patients with serious medical
OL,16,Fconditions to phone NHS 111 or 999 in
OL,17,Fan emergency.
