OL,3,CEmergency care disruption after power
OL,4,Ccut at hospital
OL,6,F"Patients are advised to attend
OL,7,Fappointments as planned tomorrow
OL,8,F(Wednesday 10 July), unless contacted
OL,9,Fand told otherwise.
OL,11,F"Visitors are welcome to attend the
OL,12,Fhospital as normal.
OL,14,F"There will be some disruption to our
OL,15,Fservices in the coming days and we are
OL,16,Fworking hard to minimise the impact on
OL,17,Fpatients.
OL,19,F"We apologise to all patients and
OL,20,Ffamilies affected by this incident."
